{"tid":1031468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3傻閪疑進食香港捕獲河豚後中毒　","createTime":"2019-02-21T16:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T16:00:15.000Z","uid":178875,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc8c65aff4ed62a0176b871de8ab948fbb31e53","tid":1031468,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190221/large/1550748982_679b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190221%2Flarge%2F1550748982_679b.jpg&h=07dbe61f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衞生防護中心建議市民應避免購買及自行宰洗河豚或不知名魚類作膳食用途，以預防河豚毒素引致的食物中毒。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心今日正調查兩宗懷疑與進食河豚有關的中毒個案，共涉及4人，當中3人曾進食在港捕獲的河豚後出現中毒徵狀，衞生防護中心強調河豚毒素不會在烹煮、風乾或冷藏過程中被分解，嚴重者可以致命，提醒市民切勿進食。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NioLWy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NioLWy&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD05YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=4876b9cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2NioLWy</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知係某蟈人定新腥港人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}